      "description": "<b>Gandalf</b><sprite name=\"commander\"><sprite name=\"emmissary\"><sprite name=\"mage\"><br>Starts with:<br>- Hobbiton <sprite name=\"pc\"/>[2]<br>- Frodo <sprite name=\"commander\"/><br>- Sam <sprite name=\"agent\"/><br>- Pippin <sprite name=\"emmissary\"/><br>- Merry <sprite name=\"agent\"/><br>- Spells <sprite name=\"spell\"/> and Artifacts <sprite name=\"artifact\"/><br><br><b>Difficulty: <mark=#ff0000>Hard</mark></b><br>- Starting power: <mark=#ff0000>Bad</mark><br>- Recruitable allies: <mark=#00ff00>Good</mark><br>- Recruitable armies: <mark=#ff0000>Bad</mark><br>- Gameplay style: character play",
      "joinedTitle": "The unexpected fate of the Ring",
      "joinedText": "Frodo… there’s something I never told you.<br><br>I always said I kept the ring with me. Every breath.<br><br>But there was one night when I took it off—just for a heartbeat. I needed silence. I meant to pick it up again immediately.<br><br>But something happened.<br><br>I must have closed my eyes. Then suddenly it was morning, and the ring was gone.<br>No sound. No trail. Just absence.<br><br>I searched. Days, maybe weeks. Time felt wrong. The harder I looked, the more it felt like the ring wasn’t lost — it had moved on.<br><br>And I’m sorry, Frodo… truly. I never meant for the burden to fall on you. But it has.<br><br>Gandalf will guide you now, my boy… where I could not.",
